  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Save water in 3 rural towns in the arid Karoo</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Trapsuutjies Environmental fixes household water leaks in 3 poor communities in the arid Klein-Karoo.  We also make communities aware of the necessity of using water sparingly and demonstrate to households how to fix minor leaks themselves, adding to sustainable water savings.  This helps to reduce the many kiloliters of unintended water losses which can be retained in highly stressed water systems.</narrative>
  </description>
